xccdf:rationale.xhtml:p:
Microsoft stores all firewall events as one file on the system (            pfirewall.log
). To improve logging, separate each firewall profile (domain, private, public) into its own distinct log file (            domainfw.log
,             privatefw.log
,             publicfw.log
) for better organization and identification of specific issues within each profile.

